sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant AI as AI Platform
    participant Hook as sync-guides.mjs
    participant Command as /arckit:pages
    
    User->>AI: /arckit:pages
    AI->>Hook: UserPromptSubmit event
    Hook->>Hook: Guard check: isRawCommand OR isExpandedBody
    
    alt Guard passes
        Hook->>Hook: Phase 1-6 execution<br/>(guide sync, scan, manifest gen)
        Hook->>Hook: Write docs/index.html
        Hook->>Hook: Write docs/manifest.json
        Hook-->>AI: additionalContext with stats
        
        AI->>Command: Execute with hook context
        Note over Command: NO tool calls<br/>Just format stats from hook
        Command-->>User: Summary output
    else Guard fails
        Hook-->>AI: (silent exit)
        AI->>Command: Execute without context
        Note over Command: Would normally scan projects,<br/>but hook didn't fire
    end
